KarassWarMachine.Description:
War Machine was once the Protoss Dragoon Taldarin's body. After Taldarin returned to Sea of World, his body was improved and he became one of the guardians of Sea of World.

Can attack the ground and air.

KarassPsionicSentry.Description:
The pilots of Psionic Sentry are Orlana and Shantira, grand preservers of the Protoss Empire. After being murdered by the swarm, their souls become guardians of Sea of the Lost World.
